History

2.1 (18.9.98)

 - Rusian Docs/Installer and Locales
 - Keyfile-System

2.0 (22.6.98)

- Patterns for general close/stay of parent window by child`s name
- Locale support
- Middle Mousebutton support in qualifierprefs

1.2 (28.5.98)

- MUI Interface
- Commodity support
- 3 different qualifier as hotkey
- Prefs saved in Tooltypes (reg)
- Hotkeyprefs
- Switch how hotkey work
- Installer
- AmigaGuide Docs

1.1 (27.5.98)

- completely rewritten in AmigaE (bug fixes and safer)
- can now be started from wb
- included lowlevel.library in archive

1.0 (20.5.98)

- first release

